<br>
Run up next to the enchanter and chain-cast chloroblast or your equivalent heal on them.  Chanter's hp goes up which is good, and I have yet to see a case in which more than 2 mobs are still on the chanter after I get 2 chloroblasts off.  You want to be next to the chanter to do this because the chanter will most likely be trying to aoe stun or aoe mezz the mobs to have a little time to get the real mez on them, so you don't want to cast from across the room and break up the grouping.  <br>
