<br>
As a side note, when a bard is mezzing, any MR debuff WILL break bardic mezz (as bardic mezz has a MR debuff associated with it).  Please don't use those spells or warn the bard that you're using Tash/Malo/etc.. prior to casting it.  Confuses the heck out of us sometimes when you miss the message in battle spam.<br>
